{
  "stem": "11179.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my parents-- I-- I wouldn't have left them if I would have known that shortly [INAUDIBLE] they were promised to get-- to get the affidavit and get the visa to the United States.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how we wound up here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "United Service for New Americans was established for getting people in that didn't have any other people guaranteeing for them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because at that time, there were strict immigration laws, not like today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and also, we came to San Francisco and they tried, because of fear of antisemitism over here, they didn't want too many people in one spot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I think in San Francisco, maybe close to 2,000 people stayed there anyway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't force them either.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They did-- they wanted to distribute them all over the whole country and found jobs for them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- wasn't a-- was a good thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But a lot of people liked it in San Francisco, found jobs there, and stayed after the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The job situation was good for everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course I had a friend here, so my parents came to Los Angeles because I had a friend here and I have an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they-- they-- who-- the people they brought in who had nobody else and-- and-- and didn't insist in staying in San Francisco-- we all came to San Francisco-- they got very good jobs, very off, all over the country.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It-- it was a wonderful thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On a ship.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was-- was one of-- one of the one of the-- I guess you call them Liberty Ships.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of the troop transporters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Marine Adder was its name, was the name of the ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, enough to get around, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Got here, got myself a job, was stu-- stuck in a trade.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
